predefinedLines.super_desc:
Heaven's Piledriver
Alpha: Deal 6 damage to an adjacent enemy. That enemy cannot use Free Movement until after the end of their next turn.

Siren's Scream
Delta: Challenge and deal 2 damage to all enemies. Then, you gain a 10-point Shield

Call In The Cavalry
Alpha: Your crew shows up to fight everybody for you! Deal 2 damage to all enemies, then deal 2 damage to all enemies.

Inspire Perfection
Delta: Remove up to 5 Common tokens from yourself and each ally you can see. Give 2 Power tokens and 2 Iron tokens to yourself and each ally you can see. You and each ally you can see heals.

Draining Knuckle
Alpha: Deal 3 damage to an adjacent enemy, and they discard all Basic Tokens they hold. Then, you gain 2 Power tokens, 2 Iron tokens, and 3 Speed tokens.

Drive Install
Delta: You gain 6 Power tokens, 6 Iron tokens, and 8 Speed tokens. For the rest of this fight, you can spend 1 more Power token and 1 more Iron token per hit. For the rest of this fight, you only discard 1 Speed token at the end of each turn, instead of all of them.

Unending Despair
Alpha: Target an adjacent enemy. Give them 4 Burning tokens, 3 Fatigue tokens, and 2 Weakness tokens. You gain 2 Iron tokens, 2 Power tokens, 2 Speed tokens, and 2 Chaos tokens.

Dancing Mad
Delta: Teleport two or three spaces, then deal 2 damage to an adjacent enemy. You may repeat this as many times as you like. After you damage the same enemy twice, you deal 1 damage to all enemies within Range 1-3, then this Super Move ends.

Erupting Burning Fist
Alpha: Deal 4 damage to an adjacent enemy, push them 4 spaces, and them them Burning Tokens until they hold 8.

Watch The World Burn
Delta: Place a Trap under each enemy you can see, then give each of those enemies 2 Burning tokes and 4 Fatigue tokens.

Sniping Point
Alpha: Your maximum range is infinite until the end of this Round. Then, deal 7 damage to an enemy within range.

Lead Rain
Delta: Target an enemy within range.
Deal 1 damage to that enemy and all adjacent enemies.
Then deal 1 damage to that enemy and all adjacent enemies.
Then deal 1 damage to that enemy and all adjacent enemies.
Then deal 1 damage to that enemy and all adjacent enemies.
Then deal 1 damage to that enemy and all adjacent enemies.

Poltergeist Panic
Alpha: You may move each Rubble or Trap you can see up to three spaces each. Each must be moved into a different space - you cannot stack opstacles on top of each other. After you've finished moving obstacles, every enemy standing on an obstacle takes 3 damage, even if it wasn't an obstacle you moved onto them.

Ghostly Possession
Delta: Target an adjacent enemy. They take the next turn slot for their side, and you control them during that turn. They cannot change Stance, and they roll their normal Action Dice for their turn. Then, you decide all Actions they take, how they move and spend tokens, and who they target with all Actions. They may declare targets as if they were on your team, for this turn only.
While you control them, they canot use any Abilities, Unique Actions, or Super Moves.
After you use this Super Move, you become Dizzy and discard all Shield you hold. You leave your Stance, you end your turn, and you cannot enter a new Stance until you take your next new turn.

Knuckle Sandwich
Alpha: Deal 4 damage to an adjacent enemy, then give them 3 Fatigue tokens, 3 Weakness tokens, and your Challenge token. Then, you may push them up to three spaces.

Everybody, Get 'Em!
Delta: Deal 4 damage to an adjacent enemy. Then, each of your allies in play may deal 3 damage to an enemy within their range.

My Final Technique
Alpha: Deal 30 damage to an enemy within range, then remove yourself from play for the rest of combat. You cannot come back.

Remember My Teachings
Delta: When you pass on your Heroic Spirit, you may declare you are using this Super Move. If you do, instead of rolling your Action Dice this turn, give them the maximum number each of those dice could have generated. Then, add an additional 8 to their numbers, give them a 4 point Shield, and they heal.

Funny Little Box of Pain
Alpha: Target an enemy at Range 2. Push everyone adjacent to the target one space. Then place walls on each space adjacent to the target, place a Deadly Trap beneath them, and give them 5 fatigue tokens.

Steal Strength
Delta: Target an adjacent character. They discard all tokens they hold, and you gain Iron tokens equal to the number of tokens discarded.

Lucky Hit
Alpha: Deal 3 damage to an adjacent enemy. Then, that enemy discards all non-Common tokens they hold, discards all Shields they hold, and cannot have Armor or Shields for the rest of this round.

Hyper Install
Delta: You gain 2 Power tokens, 2 Iron tokens, 4 Speed tokens, and heal.
For the rest of this Round, you gain a benefit at the start of every single turn, depending on whos turn it is.
If it is an enemy turn, you gain 1 Iron token and 1 Speed token.
If it is an allied turn, you gain 1 Power token and heal 1.
If it is your turn, you gain both effects, gain 1 Iron token, 1 Power token, 1 Speed token, and you heal 1.

Become My Canvas
Alpha: Deal 2 damage to an enemy within range, ignoring Armor and Shields. Then deal 2 damage to an enemy within range, ignoring Armor and Shields. Then deal 3 damage to an enemy within range, ignoring Armor and Shields.

Lightning Drop
Delta: Teleport to any space on the map.
Then, deal 4 damage to an adjacent enemy. Then, deal 2 damage to all enemies within Range 1-4.

You Are Nothing.
Alpha: Deal 4 damage to an enemy within range, pull them up to 3 spaces, and give them Weakness tokens until they hold 8.

Blizzard
Delta: Until the end of this Round, increase your maximum range by 2.
